--
--  FIXES FROM v3.7.0:
--    FIX K  — Handle hidden in first-person via Size=Vector3.zero
--             trick. Transparency/LocalTransparencyModifier are
--             unreliable on Tool handles (engine resets them).
--             Shrinking to zero size makes the part truly invisible
--             AND removes its collision box, so it cannot be seen
--             or touched. Restored to normal size in TP/unequipped.
--             A dedicated RenderStepped connection enforces the
--             size every frame so the engine cannot fight it.
--    FIX L  — Sounds: each play call clones the Sound, plays it
--             once, then Debris cleans it up. No waiting for the
--             previous instance to finish — multiple sounds can
--             overlap freely. One sound fires per place/delete.
--    FIX M  — StringValue (Name="Type", Value="Grass") added to
--             every placed block immediately on creation.
-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

